  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK352">
<l>iruṇīṅki yiṉpam payakkum maruṇīṅki</l>
<l>mācaṟu kāṭci yavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A clear, undimmed vision of things will deliver its possessors from the darkness of future births, and confer the felicity (of heaven).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
